<section class="customers py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row gx-4 align-items-start">
      <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
        <div class="p-4 blu-btn text-white rounded-3 h-100 d-flex flex-column py-5">
          <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3">Customer experiences that speak for themselves</h2>

          <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
            <h1 class="display-4 mb-0">4.9</h1>
            <div class="ms-3">
              <small class="text-light">Trusted by 30+ members</small>
              <div>
                {% for i in 1..5 %}
                  <i class="bi bi-star-fill highlight-t"></i>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-auto d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <img src="{{ alias('@web') ~ '/logo/tavola_jpg.webp' }}" alt="Logo" width="75">
            <img src="{{ alias('@web') ~ '/logo/red_carpet_jpg.webp' }}" alt="Logo" width="75">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div id="customerCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">    
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                  <img src="{{ alias('@web') ~ '/icons/seo-img.webp' }}"
                       alt="Customer"
                       class="rounded-circle mb-3"
                       width="80" height="80">
                  <span class="badge blu-btn mb-2">★ 4.0</span>
                  <h5 class="card-title mb-1">Alex Hurt</h5>
                  <small class="text-muted d-block mb-3">E-Commerce Business Owner</small>
                  <p class="card-text px-3">
                    Click Media Lab has been a game-changer for my online store. Their team developed a targeted marketing strategy that helped us increase sales by 40% in just three months. The transparency in their reporting and continuous optimization of campaigns gave us peace of mind that we were getting the best results.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                  <img src="{{ alias('@web') ~ '/icons/seo-img.webp' }}"
                       alt="Customer"
                       class="rounded-circle mb-3"
                       width="80" height="80">
                  <span class="badge bg-primary mb-2">★ 4.0</span>
                  <h5 class="card-title mb-1">Saba Vee</h5>
                  <small class="text-muted d-block mb-3">Tech Startup CEO</small>
                  <p class="card-text px-3">
                    Working with Click Media Lab has been an incredible experience. Their expertise in digital marketing helped our startup gain visibility in a competitive market. From strategy development to implementation, the team was hands-on and responsive, and we saw a significant boost in our web traffic and conversions.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#customerCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
          </button>
          <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#customerCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
          </button>
          <div class="carousel-indicators mt-4">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#customerCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#customerCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#customerCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
